00:50:53.430 --> 00:50:55.230
The thing about
the frontal cortex

00:50:55.230 --> 00:50:58.940
is that it keeps you from doing
and saying the sort of stuff

00:50:58.940 --> 00:51:01.530
that all of us contemplate
at various times,

00:51:01.530 --> 00:51:05.070
but we would die if anybody
