00:57:34.910 --> 00:57:38.840
These are individuals who
are highly regimented, highly

00:57:38.840 --> 00:57:43.150
disciplined, highly capable
of controlling their behavior.

00:57:43.150 --> 00:57:46.640
These are individuals who do not
express emotions very readily.

00:57:46.640 --> 00:57:49.810
They're very bad at reading
emotions in other people.

00:57:49.810 --> 00:57:50.830
They're not depressed.

00:57:50.830 --> 00:57:51.700
They're not anxious.

00:57:51.700 --> 00:57:54.590
In order to be labeled with
a repressive personality,

00:57:54.590 --> 00:57:55.740
