01:37:40.860 --> 01:37:45.240
Hyenas are this very interesting
case of a sex reversal

01:37:45.240 --> 01:37:46.810
androgenization.

01:37:46.810 --> 01:37:48.880
Females producing
very high levels

01:37:48.880 --> 01:37:50.810
of androgens in their ovaries.

01:37:50.810 --> 01:37:53.070
And you've got this
sex reversal system

01:37:53.070 --> 01:37:57.040
